FuncDef: This command specifies a default SLA profile for this SAP. The SLA profile must be defined prior to associating the profile with a SAP in theconfig>subscr-mgmt>sla-profilecontext.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies a default SLA profile for this SAP. The SLA profile must be defined prior to associating the profile with a SAP in the config>subscr-mgmt>sla-profile context.
